Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:27.02,sign_517_10_Student_from_my_,Note,0,0,0,,Chọn học sinh trong lớp mình để dọn phòng khoa học tự nhiên:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:27.02,sign_517_11_Nishikata,Note,0,0,0,,Nishikata
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.82,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nhớ phủi sạch cả bàn đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.24,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Dạ?!
